[SHORT DESC]
User loses 50% max HP. Maximizes Attack.

[LONG DESC]
<p>Costs the user 50% of its max HP, but brings Attack to +6 stages. It fails if the user has 50% HP or less.</p>

<p><a href="/dp/articles/belly_drum">Smogon has an article on this topic.</a>

<h2>Related Moves</h2>
<p><a href="/dp/moves/swords_dance">Swords Dance</a> only boosts Attack by two stages, but does not require 50% of the user's HP.</p>